In[579]:
def plot_line(df, title, legend=False):
    """Shows a lineplot.
    
    Args:
        df: the dataframe to plot
        title: the plot title 
    """
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 4))
    plot = sns.lineplot(x="Index", y="Value", hue="Solution", data=df)
    plt.title(title)
    plt.xlabel("Generation")
    plt.ylabel("Median fitness")
    
    if not legend:
        plot.get_legend().remove()
    
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
In[580]:
def plot_box(df, title):
    """Shows a boxplot.
    
    Args:
        df: the dataframe to plot
        title: the plot title 
    """
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 4))
    sns.boxplot(x="Solution", y="Value", data=df)
    plt.title(title)
    plt.xlabel("Solutions")
    plt.ylabel("Values")
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
In[581]:
def prepare_to_plot(df):
    """It melts a dataframe to
    plot as line or box.
    
    Args:
        df: the dataframe to transform
        
    Returns:
        DataFrame: the dataframe prepared to plot
    """
    if "Unnamed: 0" in df.columns:
        df = df.drop(columns=["Unnamed: 0"])
    df = df.reset_index().rename(columns={"index": "Index"})
    df = df.melt(id_vars=["Index"], value_vars=df.columns, var_name="Solution", value_name="Value")

    return df
